name: Cube World (itch) (Wietske)
description:
After first starting with our mobile success game: Cube Girl. It is now time for the next step. CUBE WORLD. Now Cube Girl is in 3D and the world is even more dangerous than before! Complete the different challenges and get the highest score!

This is a work in progress so it may not be everything that it could be now, but we hope you will still enjoy our early development prototype. For suggestions, questions or anything else, we would love the feedback!
